		(property "Description" "The 5PB1102 is a high-performance 1:2 LVCMOS clock buffer. It has best-in-class Additive Phase Jitter of 50fsec RMS.The 5PB1102also supports an Output Enable function. It is available in 8-pin DFN and TSSOP packages and can operate from a 1.8V to 3.3V supply."
